[3m[2m// Todo: Check associativity https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Operator_Precedence[0m
[3m[2m// Todo: Right now you can put any type of Expression on the lhs of a variableAssignment like: 5 = y; We only want to do this for a few cases however[0m
[3m[2m// Rather than exclude everything other than those cases it would be much easier to whitelist the few that ARE allowed.[0m
[1msyntax[0m Expression
    = array: "[" {Expression ","}* elements ","? "]"
    | objectDefinition: "{" {PropertyAssignment ","}* properties ","? "}"
    | this: "this"
