[3m[2m// This production wrapper encodes what the lookahead set is for the productions it wraps[0m
[1mpublic[0m [1mdata[0m Production
    = lookahead(Symbol def, [1mset[0m[Symbol] classes, Production production);
[1mpublic[0m [1mdata[0m Symbol = eoi();
