[3m[2m// TODO: The following function was defined local to optimizeLookaheads[0m
[3m[2m// but this gives a not yet explained validation error for the[0m
[3m[2m// function ids in the corresponding overloaded function[0m
[1mlist[0m[CharRange] order([1mlist[0m[CharRange] x) {
    [1mreturn[0m sort([e | e <- x, e != \empty-range()], lessThan);
